             was indicted for <rs id="t18220911-279-off1466" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220911-279-off1466" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-279-off1466" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220911-279-cd1467" type="crimeDate">23d of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-279-off1466 t18220911-279-cd1467"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-279-off1468 t18220911-279-cd1467"></join>, at St. Marylebone, one watch, value 5 l.; one chain, value 1 l.; five seals, value 30 s.; and one key, value 1 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220911-279-victim2542" type="victimName">
                           Charles Lewis 
                           Spitta
                        <interp inst="t18220911-279-victim2542" type="surname" value="Spitta"></interp>
